    {
      "name": "Dashboard (hotel)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Hotel dashboard metrics",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{accessToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dashboard/metrics?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "dashboard", "metrics"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "from", "value": "2026-01-01" },
                { "key": "to", "value": "2026-01-31" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Métricas agregadas para el hotel vinculado al usuario (Auth `hotel_id`). Roles **HOTEL** / **MANAGER**, o **TRAVELER** si existe fila en `users.hotel_user` (seed: `maria@example.com` → Cadena del Sol).\n\n**Si obtienes 404 HTML de nginx:** el gateway no tiene la ruta nueva; en el repo ejecuta `docker compose up -d --force-recreate thub-gateway` (o `docker compose down` + `up`) para remontar `backend/nginx/nginx.conf`.\n\n**Base de datos:** si el volumen de Postgres ya existía antes del seed nuevo, aplica el `INSERT` de `hotel_user` de María o recrea el volumen (`docker compose down -v`)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — ejemplo",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dashboard/metrics?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31"
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"metrics\": {\n    \"totalBookings\": { \"value\": 3, \"variation\": 50.0 },\n    \"revenue\": { \"value\": 1200.5, \"variation\": 12.5 },\n    \"occupancyRate\": { \"value\": 45.2, \"variation\": -5.0 },\n    \"averageRating\": { \"value\": 4.3, \"variation\": 10.0 }\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "403 — viajero",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dashboard/metrics?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31"
              },
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"Las métricas de hotel requieren una cuenta vinculada a un hotel.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Revenue report by period",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{accessToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dashboard/revenue-report?hotel_id={{hotelId}}&from={{reportFrom}}&to={{reportTo}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "dashboard", "revenue-report"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "hotel_id", "value": "{{hotelId}}" },
                { "key": "from", "value": "{{reportFrom}}" },
                { "key": "to", "value": "{{reportTo}}" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Genera reporte de ingresos para un hotel y rango de fechas.\n\n**Parámetros:** `hotel_id`, `from`, `to`.\n\n**Auth:** roles `HOTEL` o `MANAGER` con token Bearer (`{{accessToken}}`).\n\n**Notas de negocio:**\n- `totalRevenue` usa pagos con estado `CAPTURED`.\n- `adr = totalRevenue / sold_room_nights`.\n- `occupancyRate` se calcula con noches ocupadas sobre capacidad del período.\n- `variation` compara contra período anterior equivalente (misma duración, inmediatamente anterior).\n"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — ejemplo",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dashboard/revenue-report?hotel_id={{hotelId}}&from={{reportFrom}}&to={{reportTo}}"
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"kpis\": {\n    \"totalRevenue\": { \"value\": 124530.0, \"variation\": 12.5 },\n    \"adr\": { \"value\": 345.0, \"variation\": 4.2 },\n    \"occupancyRate\": { \"value\": 82.4, \"variation\": -1.8 }\n  },\n  \"trends\": [\n    { \"date\": \"2026-10-01\", \"revenue\": 4500.0, \"occupancyRate\": 78.0 },\n    { \"date\": \"2026-10-02\", \"revenue\": 5200.0, \"occupancyRate\": 80.5 }\n  ],\n  \"revenueByRoomType\": [\n    { \"roomType\": \"Deluxe Suite\", \"unitsSold\": 145, \"avgRate\": 320.0, \"totalRevenue\": 46400.0 },\n    { \"roomType\": \"Standard Double\", \"unitsSold\": 312, \"avgRate\": 185.0, \"totalRevenue\": 57720.0 }\n  ],\n  \"totalAggregatedRevenue\": 104120.0,\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"from\": \"2026-10-01\",\n    \"to\": \"2026-10-31\",\n    \"currency\": \"USD\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "403 — hotel_id no autorizado",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dashboard/revenue-report?hotel_id=ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff&from={{reportFrom}}&to={{reportTo}}"
              },
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"No autorizado para consultar reportes de este hotel.\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "400 — rango inválido",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
